          ## GNARBOX (Part 1)

          When you own a camera, the biggest problem is managing all of your HD videos and photos. GNARBOX solves this problem by allowing you to backup, edit and share all of your footage, without a laptop. <em>2,988 Kickstarter backers pledged $540,776 to bring this project to life</em>.

