          #### Organising media

          <em>GNARBOX automatically organises media based on the date the files were created</em>. For example, if you went skiing on 9th November, GNARBOX would create a folder called “November 9” and add the files to it.

          Files are then organised by time inside each folder. So if you were skiing at one location in the morning, then another location in the afternoon, your photos and videos will be grouped accordingly.

