          #### Importing files

          If you have 2 SD cards plugged in, not only can you import files from those cards into GNARBOX, but you can also directly move files between each card. When viewing content on an SD card, files that aren’t backed up are given priority. <em>Allowing customers to easily see which files they need to import</em>.

